The Quick and the Dead, (orig. title: One by One, released in 1975) is a documentary about the deadliness of Grand Prix racing, including footage of fatal racing accidents. It is narrated by Stacy Keach.The film was reissued as "The Quick and the Dead" in 1978 including the death of Tom Pryce at the 1977 South African Grand Prix. and was later released also as "Champions Forever: The Formula One Drivers".